        "subject": "LU-0000 tests: perform failover test",
        "message": "LU-0000 tests: perform failover test\n\nThis is for test only.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly \\\nenvdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,REQFAIL=100,DURATION=28800 \\\nclientdistro=el6 ossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nossarch=x86_64 mdsarch=x86_64 \\\nclientcount=4 osscount=2 mdscount=2 \\\nmdssizegb=10 ostsizegb=10 \\\nausteroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\ntestlist=recovery-mds-scale,recovery-random-scale,recovery-double-scale,mmp\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6dc5f809fbf5f0c7d4343b11c29feaac90c18a75\n"
      },
